'From Squeak3.2alpha of 26 December 2001 [latest update: #4599] on 26 December 2001 at 9:38:38 am'!"Change Set:		Change Set: setVersionFIX-jetDate:			26 December 2001Author:			John ToblerFixes a minor 'Date not indexable' bug in SystemVersion setVersion."!!SystemVersion class methodsFor: 'class initialization' stamp: 'jet 12/26/2001 09:25'!setVersion	"SystemVersion setVersion"	| newName |	newName _ FillInTheBlank		request: ('Please name this system version.\The old version is:\',					self current version, '\set on ', self current date asString) withCRs 		initialAnswer: self current version.	newName size > 0 ifTrue:		[self newVersion: newName]! !